        Over <strong>23 years</strong> designing and delivering enterprise-scale SAP solutions
        for global organizations. S/4HANA migrations. Field Service Management.
        Complex system integrations across BTP, CPI, and OTC processes.<br /><br />
        This is not a background. This is a <strong>structural advantage</strong>.
        Every agent system I design and every workflow I architect is built on decades of knowing
