        In 2026, I started over deliberately. Studying for the
        <strong>Claude Certified Architect (CCA) Foundations exam</strong>,
        Anthropic's first official AI architecture certification.<br /><br />
        But I did not just study quietly. I built a <strong>CCA study app, now available at /architect-zero/</strong>.
        I launched a <strong>YouTube learning series</strong> to teach every lesson the day I learned it.
        I brought my family - a 13-year-old, a 17-year-old, and a non-IT adult - along for the ride.<br /><br />
        <strong>Architect Zero</strong> is the live study system behind that journey:
        lessons, quizzes, flashcards, progress tracking, and a repeatable path from zero to certified.
